snippet.title: Intro to Bally Midway NFL Football Raiders vs. Chargers (White Caddy) Arcade CED (Better Quality)
snippet.description:
This is only the intro to the white caddy NFL arcade CED, just in better quality and being played back in straight stereo. This gives you a chance to hear how the audio is truly recorded on the disc--the entire disc is encoded as dual-audio. The uploads of the entire disc are still on my channel.

There is a lot of black space before the teaser--I edited most of that out, but kept the black space after the teaser intact so you can see how much of a space there is. Don't know why there is a slight 'pop' after the teaser, I think it was just a slight glitch when recording.
